Use plain, direct engineering language.

This is a static Vite and React application published from docs/.
Author static discovery resources in public/ and run npm run build before publishing.

Do not claim that GRA Release Radar has a hosted analysis API, live MCP transport, OAuth server, CLI, SDK, webhook endpoint, or streaming endpoint unless that capability exists in the repository and is deployed.

Before shipping changes, run:

- npm test
- npm run typecheck
- npm run build
